reviewText: Excellent info provided. Enjoyable to watch and learn
Ok, some info if you listen for it but it doesn't overflow.
Very informational.. My son is a huge fishermen and learned a lot..
have not actually seen it but each year my grandson requests more In-Fisherman videos... He loves them
Gave this to my fiance' for Christmas and he was very pleased. He said it was very informative, and as an experienced fisherman, said he actually learned new tactics. Buy it!
